videos.description: Alex Robinson comes off the screen and lobs it up for Kevin Samuel, who rocks the rim with a strong alley-oop finish.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Robinson lobs, Samuel slams for TCU) 2019/02/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson lobs, Samuel slams for TCU

videos.description: but Cameron Lard cleans it up a missed layup with a nasty dunk and follows that up by later getting another putback jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Lard throws down two huge putbacks for Cyclones) 2019/02/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lard throws down two huge putbacks for Cyclones

videos.description: Talen Horton-Tucker blows by Kouat Noi and drives baseline for the huge one-handed reverse slam, cutting into TCU's lead late in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Iowa State's Horton-Tucker hammers down reverse dunk) 2019/02/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa State's Horton-Tucker hammers down reverse dunk

videos.description: Desmond Bane dumps off a pass to JD Miller, who powers through the contact to finish a clutch and-1 and extend TCU's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Miller banks home clutch and-1 for Horned Frogs) 2019/02/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Miller banks home clutch and-1 for Horned Frogs
